wiki.content:
Beneath Your Beautiful" is a song by British singers Labrinth and Emeli Sandé. Written by Labrinth, Mike Posner and Sandé, it was released as the sixth single from Labrinth's debut album, Electronic Earth, on October 21, 2012. The track peaked at #1 on the UK Singles Chart, selling 108,000 copies in the week of release, to become Labrinth's first ever number one single
